<doc title="Updating files in Working copy">
    <section>
        <hr></hr>
        <p>
           Update brings changes from the repository into your working copy. <br />
           It brings your working copy up-to-date with the HEAD (latest) revision from the repository. 
            <br /><br /><br />
            <img src="../../img/ws_right_click_menu.png" align="left" />
            <list>
                <item>1. Open the solution/project you want to work with. </item>
                <item>2. Right click on a item you want to update.</item>
                <item>3. Select 'Update' from the menu.</item>
                <item></item>
            </list>
            <br clear="all" />
         </p>
    </section>
